td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Directive 2004/35/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 21 April 2004 on environmental liability with regard to the prevention and remedying of environmental damage (
OJ 2004 L 143, p. 56
), as amended by Directive 2009/31/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 23 April 2009 (
OJ 2009 L 140, p. 114
) (‘Directive 2004/35’) and Article 4(7) of Directive 2000/60/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 23 October 2000 establishing a framework for Community action in the field of water policy (
OJ 2000 L 327, p. 1
).
